prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist 2D flat illustration of a birthday scene. On a clean, solid light cream background, feature cartoon versions of the two people from the reference photo. Jordan (person on the right) is still wearing his graduation gown and stole (without any text), but instead of a graduation cap, he's humorously wearing a pointy birthday party hat that is comically small for his head. He has a big, happy, slightly goofy smile. Lao Lao (person on the left) is wearing her white dress and is playfully placing a single, lit birthday candle on top of his party hat, looking at him with a loving and amused expression. A few simple, colorful confetti shapes are floating gently around them.

Centered below the couple, in an elegant, readable, handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my favorite graduate, Jordan"
